	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Curacao</placeName> <date>11th Septr. 1852</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">I last had this pleasure on<lb/> the <date>27th</date> Ulto&#58; since then I have received yours under date<lb/> <date>2nd Augt.</date> together with the &#8220;Occidents&#8221; of that month&#44; and<lb/> the nine numbers of <date>Augt.</date> &#38; <date>Septe. 1851</date>&#44; these have arrived<lb/> at a good time to enable me to make the collections for<lb/> the same.  I have shown the page of your Bible to<lb/> several of our Members&#44; all like the print <add>Hebrew</add>.  I have<lb/> therefore to request of you to send me a few extra copies<lb/> to those subscribed for in your prospectus&#44; as I am sure<lb/> to dispose of them&#44; I would recommend a few unbound<lb/> and a few bound neatly.  I am in hopes of soon giving<lb/> you a more favorable report of our subscribers for your<lb/> Periodical&#44; and shall use my efforts to influence our<lb/> People to promote your labours.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have noticed your remarks relative to your prayer<lb/> books&#44; and shall in conformity execute your wishes&#44; as<lb/> soon as a favorable opportunity offers itself&#44; this vessel<lb/> leaves this for <add>&#63;</add>oro under charter&#44; which prevents me from<lb/> fulfilling your order now.  I shall try all in my<lb/> power to procure and forward you the Citiora &#38; Lulabion<add>&#63;</add><lb/> as soon as possible&#44; the Brig &#8220;Abrue&#8221;<add>&#63;</add> is expected here</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>in a few days&#44; by her I hope to be able to send them.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My brother in Law <persName>Nathan</persName> tenders you his best<lb/> wishes&#44; and joins me with my family Circle in wishing<lb/> you many happy returns of our approaching Holy days&#44;<lb/> with best wishes for your health &#38; happiness.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am very truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Yours</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Moses Lindo</persName></p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>CURACAO</placeName></p>
		</body>
